    <img src="rainforest.jpg" alt="the rainforest">
    <div class="infotext">
    <p>Did you know that in the past the land was covered by 14% rainforest and now it is only covered by 6%?
      <br> 8% of the earth’s rainforests have been cut down for agricultural use and for palm oil plantations. The rainforest is important for everyone, yet no one cares for it.

