<h5 id="en">Water rising</h5>
  <div class="informationsbokse">

    <img src="water.jpg" alt="Iceberg melting">
    <div class="infotext">

    <p>The water level will rise above 1 meter to 2100 meter if we continue to emit CO2 as we do now.  20% of the world's population who are living on small islands, in low-lying countries with long coastlines or close to melting glaciers, will be flooded.
