<h5 id="en">Oil in the sea</h5>

  <div class="informationsbokse">
    <img src="oil.jpg" alt="taking oil from the underground">
    <div class="infotext">
    <p>3 Sources of Oil Pollution:
Natural leakage, an example is leakage from factories.
Cars and other vehicles, many vehicles have escaping oil which evaporates and with the rain can end in the sea.
Yachts, or other pleasure craft, like cars can escape oil, here it ends up directly in the sea.

<br> <a href="#">Read more</a>
